				The ghasts drop hearts about 1 in 5 times. Undead are the placeholders, both wandering and the ones at the obelisk. You need four hearts for part of a quest for Druids/Clerics with Tunare religion to get a no mana root necklace! I think it's called Warden symbol of Tunare. Look it up under Felwithe quests. The ghasts are fairly rare, killing all the undead in the zone, one would spawn per 30 minutes or hour. Worse yet, they dropped the heart about 1 in 5 times. I've gotten two hearts and in that time I've killed Thistle EIGHT times. :P  Can't wait til I get outta here!<BR>
